/*EXI *  TEXT('Midas MM Validate deal subtype')
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  Midas - Money Market Dealing Module                          *
      *                                                               *
      *  MMVDLSTYPE - Validate deal subtype                           *
      *                                                               *
      *  Function:  This module receives a parameter containing a     *
      *             putative deal subtype, and confirms whether it is *
      *             a valid Money Market subtype or not.  If it is    *
      *             valid the 10A return code will be blank; if it    *
      *             is not it will contain 'Error'                    *
      *                                                               *
      *  Component of: MMVALIDTE - MM validation service program      *
      *                                                               *
      *  (c) Finastra International Limited 2001                      *
      *                                                               *
